Good afternoon Chris, you helped me with a sailing plan in Sweden this year.
For the next year we would like to organize a sailing in the Norwegian
fjords, with two boats. It is very early, but last year we tried to
organize around October-November and it was already too late, so we would
like to play it in advance.
Can you help? We are looking for a nice panoramic route in the fjords, with
two sailboats with 3 double cabins each. Period: July, preferably 10-17
(Saturday to Saturday) but we can accommodate other dates.
Thank you for your help.

-- 
